佢成長<br />\n<br />\n問題係其他人追佢都追唔到<br />\n一個靚女單身四年<br />\n係因為左諗右諗怕左先唔拍拖<br />\n<br />\n但我個半月就追到手<br />\n<br />\n有時諗到底係 經驗豐富令佢揀我<br />\n定 佢真係鐘意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc7c8f67a0d17bdcd1245389b8cdda5c4694470","tid":37310,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:49:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>習慣咗做兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知算唔算兵<br />\n但呢刻到我唔想答應<br />\n<br />\n我本身係個playboy<br />\n依家唔想再拍散拖<br />\n如果佢對我係仰慕 唔係鐘意<br />\n我都唔知開唔開始好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我懂的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你有冇試"},{"pid":"f3ec0cbd32d3df4cadafcdd631a228a5815cef5c","tid":37310,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}